@danny0405 
It is hard to maintain this PR. Despite the fact that this feature is related only to flink, changes are needed in common part. For example, https://github.com/apache/hudi/pull/5830#discussion_r1023681719 and https://github.com/apache/hudi/pull/5830#discussion_r1022504653
Because of this, merge conflicts often appear. Currently, `HoodieMergeHelper.java` both modified again. I've decided that **I will make common part changes in separate PRs**. I hope that such changes will be quickly approved and merged into master branch. That will reduce the number of conflicts and make it easier to maintain this PR as well as reviewing the code.
